name: Baby Maria Super Hero Girl Dress Up - cool fashion dressing game

description:
Welcome to the virtual baby beauty contest! Make your princess baby maria shine like a fashion star. Compete with other beauty queen contestants and win first prize.
And yes you become the miss universe.
Aww What a beautiful dream i saw last night.
Don’t worry we will fulfill your dream of becoming a super model a fashion icon.
Choose best modern clothing style for maria.
You can participate in fashion show anytime.
Put on style which makes you a super star model.
Mismatch dress with glamour accessories, top hairstyles, brand new necklace,earrings, stilettos.

Features:
=> Turn your beauty into fashionable model.
=> Pick best modeling dress among all huge collection.
=> Match your dress with jewelry and bags.
=> Share your star girl look.
